	title="Templates"
	lede="Reusable starting points for docs, decks, launch notes, and project checklists."
	sections={[
		{
			heading: "Doc Scaffold",
			body: "Title, one-sentence purpose, short context, and clear next steps. Keep pages skim-friendly.",
